 in your enlisted pay grade, the more you see that big picture. I'm

00:01:03.150 --> 00:01:07.600
 an E7, so my responsibility is to know how this unit can help the

00:01:07.600 --> 00:01:12.050
 civilians, make sure that this aircraft carrier runs fine and I think

00:01:12.050 --> 00:01:16.500
 as officers, the higher you get, if you're a captain, you make sure

00:01:16.500 --> 00:01:20.950
 that this aircraft carrier fits in this realm of the region so that,

00:01:20.950 --> 00:01:25.400
 like we have power over there, we can dominate our foes. So, it depends

